WEBVTT

00:05.805 --> 00:06.973
[soft rumbling]

00:17.884 --> 00:20.987
♪♪♪

01:31.191 --> 01:32.725
Good to have you back.

01:32.792 --> 01:34.194
Marquis, sir.

01:38.865 --> 01:41.134
♪♪♪

01:58.118 --> 02:01.287
♪♪♪

02:07.026 --> 02:08.094
[panting]

02:13.633 --> 02:15.235
[knocking]

02:18.505 --> 02:20.440
[knocking]

02:23.042 --> 02:24.611
[knocking]

02:27.680 --> 02:29.449
- Olivia!
- May I come in?

02:29.516 --> 02:31.117
Yes, are you okay?

02:32.585 --> 02:34.487
Olivia, what happened?

02:34.554 --> 02:37.123
That scumbag Zhou
tried to kill me.

02:37.190 --> 02:38.725
Screw Zhou.

02:38.791 --> 02:41.528
I'm alive, and I know
where the girls are.

03:02.282 --> 03:04.317
Nothing.
It's impossible to penetrate.

03:04.384 --> 03:06.986
That's a fucking fortress.

03:07.086 --> 03:09.589
Shit.

03:09.689 --> 03:11.391
The only option left
is to get in from below.

03:11.491 --> 03:14.327
From below?

03:17.764 --> 03:19.332
I'd say it's less
than half a mile

03:19.399 --> 03:21.568
from this point
to this point.

03:21.634 --> 03:23.636
PAULA: I thought the tunnels
were totally closed.

03:23.703 --> 03:26.039
'Cause most of them
were walled up or collapsed.

03:26.105 --> 03:28.641
Yeah, and what's left standing
is a real labyrinth.

03:28.708 --> 03:30.343
But do you have a better idea?

03:47.794 --> 03:49.996
If anything happens,
get us out, please.

03:50.096 --> 03:51.831
We've only got you, my friend.

03:51.931 --> 03:54.534
You just bring back my girl.
I'll take care of the rest.

03:54.601 --> 03:55.969
Thank you, Roca.

03:57.103 --> 03:58.905
Let's go that way.

03:59.005 --> 04:00.273
This way.

04:07.547 --> 04:09.282
- This way, hurry.
- You sure, Costa?

04:09.349 --> 04:12.352
Yeah.

04:12.452 --> 04:14.053
This must be it.

04:17.156 --> 04:19.425
There. Follow me, yeah,
this way, let's go!

04:20.393 --> 04:22.829
MARIO: Watch out!
Watch out!

04:22.929 --> 04:25.398
[whirring]

04:38.077 --> 04:40.280
It looks kinda dangerous, right?

04:40.346 --> 04:41.481
I mean, look at her.

04:41.547 --> 04:44.150
- It's pretty much like a...
- Possession.

04:44.250 --> 04:46.519
ZETA: But is this your plan
to take us to the spa?

04:46.586 --> 04:47.320
QUINO: To get possessed?

04:47.387 --> 04:49.822
[burping]
That's right.

04:49.922 --> 04:51.891
QUINO: You'd be the host
and guest.

04:51.958 --> 04:52.725
"Evil Dead,"
"The Amityville Horror."

04:52.792 --> 04:54.961
Doesn't that ring a bell?

04:55.028 --> 04:58.131
Yeah, right, whatever.
But do you think

04:58.197 --> 05:01.034
that with this voodoo shit,
we'll be able get out of town?

05:01.134 --> 05:02.335
Well, no fucking idea,
but we'll have to try,

05:02.402 --> 05:05.705
because I won't just
sit here scratching my ass

05:05.805 --> 05:07.507
while my friend is having
a bad time in that hole.

05:09.075 --> 05:10.109
It's time to go.

05:10.209 --> 05:11.244
Javi, are you in?

05:12.612 --> 05:14.047
Yes.

05:14.113 --> 05:15.848
And what about the rest of us?

05:15.915 --> 05:17.283
QUINO: We're gonna be
the backup.

05:17.350 --> 05:18.785
We'll be Han Solo.

05:18.885 --> 05:20.320
We'll keep watch from the road,
we might see

05:20.386 --> 05:21.654
something from there.

05:23.489 --> 05:25.525
This is the final battle, guys!

05:27.493 --> 05:28.795
What's wrong, Javi?

05:34.934 --> 05:36.836
Do you want us to leave?

05:40.239 --> 05:42.608
What?

05:42.675 --> 05:44.677
If it wasn't for you guys,
I would not be here.

05:44.744 --> 05:46.546
No, no, no, no, no.
Hell no, dude.

05:46.646 --> 05:47.947
But that place is gonna be
crawling with revenants.

05:48.047 --> 05:49.816
No, damn it,
we're not going anywhere.

05:49.882 --> 05:52.285
Quino, you can't do anything.

05:52.352 --> 05:52.919
We'll wait for you
to come back.

05:56.556 --> 05:56.923
What if I don't make it?

06:00.693 --> 06:00.927
No.

06:03.196 --> 06:04.797
No, no, you'll come back.

06:04.864 --> 06:06.366
You'll meet us right here
and we'll leave together

06:06.432 --> 06:06.966
through that telephone booth.

06:29.989 --> 06:30.990
OLIVIA: Are you guys done
blowing each other yet?

06:37.029 --> 06:39.465
I'm just saying that because
we have to leave, you know.

07:08.428 --> 07:08.961
Olivia?

07:30.316 --> 07:31.517
[chuckles lightly]

07:37.056 --> 07:39.292
PAULA: Watch your step.
MARIO: Yeah.

07:42.395 --> 07:44.864
I think it's this way.
Yeah.

07:52.805 --> 07:54.273
Okay, this is--
this way here, Mario.

07:54.373 --> 07:56.609
I think.

07:58.611 --> 07:59.045
MARIO: Hurry.

08:01.080 --> 08:02.415
PAULA: Oh, shit.

08:02.482 --> 08:05.485
MAN: Check down that side
of the perimeter.

09:06.112 --> 09:07.079
Yes! Yes! Yes!

09:09.348 --> 09:10.917
[laughing]

09:14.654 --> 09:16.956
PAULA: Hold on.

09:19.592 --> 09:22.495
Okay, come.

09:24.430 --> 09:24.964
This way.

09:35.708 --> 09:38.110
[panting]

09:42.915 --> 09:44.383
Damn it!

09:44.483 --> 09:46.118
Fuck, fuck, fuck!

10:00.533 --> 10:02.802
[car starting]

10:19.285 --> 10:21.787
[phone ringing]

11:10.403 --> 11:14.206
Since your brother passed away,
you're all she has.

11:16.876 --> 11:17.910
It's all right.
Cheer up, kid.

11:19.845 --> 11:21.213
Come with me.

11:43.769 --> 11:45.504
I'm sorry.

11:48.708 --> 11:50.209
I'm sorry.

11:57.717 --> 11:57.983
ANTONIO: Where is the bread?

12:00.453 --> 12:01.787
Thank you.

12:05.291 --> 12:08.294
♪♪♪

12:58.410 --> 13:00.846
[high-pitch ringing]

13:20.633 --> 13:21.767
- Hey!
- [gasps]

13:21.834 --> 13:23.502
What's happening, guys?

13:23.602 --> 13:24.870
They cut the power.
They're coming for us.

13:24.970 --> 13:26.639
Time to get the hell
out of here!

13:26.705 --> 13:29.074
[phone ringing]

13:29.175 --> 13:31.076
You live in
fucking anxiety, dude.

13:37.149 --> 13:39.852
[ringing continues]

13:46.492 --> 13:50.262
It's not only in the town,
it's along the entire coast.

13:51.230 --> 13:54.366
You mean, because of the spa?

13:54.433 --> 13:56.368
What if the blackout
is connected?

13:57.369 --> 13:58.604
Javi!

13:58.671 --> 14:00.072
He's heading down a rathole.

14:00.172 --> 14:02.074
There's nothing
we can do for him.

14:02.174 --> 14:03.876
We can try to switch
the light on.

14:03.976 --> 14:05.511
Man, do you really think
there's a button you can push

14:05.611 --> 14:07.112
- that says "spa lighting on"?
- There is.

14:07.213 --> 14:09.949
Fifteen minutes away
at the power station.

14:10.049 --> 14:12.151
I used to go with my father.

14:12.251 --> 14:14.320
But still,
we can't touch shit, man!

14:14.386 --> 14:16.455
How the hell are we gonna push
a power button?

14:16.522 --> 14:17.590
I don't know,
but at least we gotta try.

14:17.690 --> 14:20.593
Javi did it once.

14:20.693 --> 14:22.394
We'll try to find a way.

14:22.494 --> 14:24.830
I'm not ditching
my friend here.

14:24.930 --> 14:26.065
I'll do everything I can, dude.

14:28.601 --> 14:30.269
So, what do you say?
[ringing continues]

14:30.369 --> 14:32.438
Zeta?

14:34.106 --> 14:36.175
Where did you say
the power station is?

14:52.591 --> 14:54.026
[high-pitch ringing]

15:10.743 --> 15:12.211
It's this way.

15:16.882 --> 15:17.983
Oh, fuck!

15:18.918 --> 15:20.052
Damn it.

15:21.320 --> 15:22.521
Come on.

15:24.690 --> 15:24.957
What the hell?

15:28.394 --> 15:31.330
What the hell?
Damn it!

15:34.466 --> 15:36.268
According to the map,
the spa is right there,

15:36.368 --> 15:38.070
just on the other side
of this wall!

15:39.571 --> 15:42.174
Just forget it.
We can't go any further.

15:42.241 --> 15:44.476
Let me think, we'll come up
with something.

15:44.543 --> 15:45.311
We won't come up
with anything.

15:45.411 --> 15:48.347
Mario.

15:48.447 --> 15:50.115
What are we doing, Costa?

15:50.215 --> 15:51.850
[Paula sighs]

15:51.917 --> 15:54.653
It's just a waste of time.
Sandra's passed away.

15:54.720 --> 15:56.188
No.
No, she's not.

15:56.288 --> 15:58.223
Mario.
Mario, where are you going?

15:58.324 --> 16:00.225
We need to get them
out of there!

16:03.862 --> 16:05.397
Mario.

16:07.333 --> 16:09.001
Sandra's dead, Paula.

16:10.402 --> 16:12.104
I can't take this anymore.

16:25.551 --> 16:27.920
Beat them
at their own game.

16:27.987 --> 16:28.921
Look for the flaw.

16:39.198 --> 16:40.966
MAN: Keep moving to the spa.

16:42.434 --> 16:44.136
Come on, keep moving.

17:34.053 --> 17:36.388
Hey!
Keep it moving!

17:54.206 --> 17:56.375
Your daughter is still alive!

17:56.442 --> 17:59.678
My gut's telling me so,
and I'll prove it to you!

18:05.150 --> 18:07.119
[gunshots]

18:07.186 --> 18:09.388
Costa!
Costa, what are you doing?

18:23.068 --> 18:25.571
♪♪♪

19:08.647 --> 19:10.015
[whispering]
Let's go.

19:17.956 --> 19:19.424
[gasping]

19:40.112 --> 19:43.649
[chanting]

19:43.715 --> 19:46.185
♪♪♪

20:23.789 --> 20:25.824
[creaking]

20:42.975 --> 20:45.444
Zhou isn't here.
Shall we wait for him?

20:45.510 --> 20:47.446
He knows the rules very well.

21:17.175 --> 21:18.443
[chanting]

21:18.510 --> 21:22.714
♪♪♪

21:38.830 --> 21:40.932
Those are Alvaro's parents.

21:44.469 --> 21:46.004
PAULA: Those motherfuckers.

21:48.440 --> 21:49.041
[match striking]

21:58.850 --> 22:00.652
[shrieking]

22:04.589 --> 22:05.924
JAVI: Olivia!.

22:10.696 --> 22:11.663
What's wrong?

22:11.763 --> 22:13.065
It doesn't matter.

22:13.165 --> 22:16.201
- You have to go on alone.
- But why?

22:18.904 --> 22:20.639
Is that what happened
to your grandma?

22:21.673 --> 22:24.609
You knew about it.

22:24.676 --> 22:27.312
Go down into that cellar
and get the girls out.

22:27.412 --> 22:28.080
Please.

22:30.048 --> 22:31.950
Go on.
Javi, please go!

22:49.634 --> 22:52.104
♪♪♪

25:35.734 --> 25:38.069
[sobbing]

25:48.713 --> 25:51.216
[door opens]

25:57.989 --> 25:59.524
Don't give me that look, girls.

26:02.494 --> 26:04.329
You all should be very proud
to be a part

26:04.396 --> 26:06.131
of something like this.

26:07.799 --> 26:10.535
And I thank you
for the gift you offer us.

26:16.908 --> 26:18.043
You're such a treasure.

26:23.348 --> 26:25.884
More valuable
than the Library of Alexandria,

26:25.951 --> 26:28.086
more than the World Bank's fund.

26:29.554 --> 26:31.289
More than all the gold
in the world.

26:31.356 --> 26:34.192
You are strikingly
valuable, girls.

26:34.292 --> 26:36.928
You give us the most coveted
thing in the history of mankind.

26:40.799 --> 26:41.933
Precious time.

26:43.935 --> 26:46.605
And that's the shit,
that's the fucking shit.

26:46.671 --> 26:49.240
because time
makes the impossible possible.

26:49.307 --> 26:53.812
We only use a part of our brain,
and then we die.

26:53.878 --> 26:58.917
Now, imagine just for a moment
that we could live forever.

26:58.984 --> 27:01.386
What we could achieve
would be unimaginable.

27:02.721 --> 27:05.390
[high-pitch ringing]

27:09.761 --> 27:12.197
We could control the human will,
for example.

27:14.532 --> 27:15.934
I need you to understand me.

27:16.001 --> 27:18.203
When I see you fighting
against evolution,

27:18.269 --> 27:19.604
it breaks my heart,
it really hurts me.

27:19.671 --> 27:23.475
Cause we put an end
to the plague, to tuberculosis.

27:23.575 --> 27:25.677
We made penicillin a reality.

27:25.744 --> 27:27.345
Hell, we actually
discovered insulin.

27:27.445 --> 27:29.848
You should know about that.

27:29.914 --> 27:32.083
We have saved
thousands of lives.

27:35.153 --> 27:37.522
Those lives are no less
than yours.

27:52.103 --> 27:54.039
I hope you girls understand.

28:30.975 --> 28:34.412
[chanting]

28:34.479 --> 28:37.048
♪♪♪

29:15.954 --> 29:17.489
You made it.

29:53.558 --> 29:55.093
[sighs]

31:13.872 --> 31:16.641
[whispering]
Mario, Mario.

31:16.708 --> 31:19.711
Listen to me, we're gonna
get them out of here, okay?

31:19.811 --> 31:21.646
But you must do what I say.

31:21.713 --> 31:22.914
Mario.

31:40.431 --> 31:41.833
QUINO: Hey, guys!

31:48.239 --> 31:51.009
Even if we could touch it,
it'd be useless.

31:51.075 --> 31:53.645
Those motherfuckers
burned it out.

31:53.711 --> 31:55.680
Man, this is fucked up.

31:58.049 --> 31:59.183
ALVARO: So, now what?

32:02.520 --> 32:06.958
♪♪♪

33:08.519 --> 33:11.923
[car starting]

33:11.990 --> 33:14.192
MAN ON RADIO: [muffled]The
director of Banesto team...

33:35.046 --> 33:35.847
They're gonna drown the girls.

33:35.913 --> 33:38.016
No, no, no, no, no.
Mario.

33:45.089 --> 33:47.325
Even if you think
she's going to die,

33:47.392 --> 33:49.360
you have to trust me,
you have to wait.

33:52.563 --> 33:53.931
Okay?

33:57.969 --> 34:00.371
[panicked breathing]

34:08.646 --> 34:11.883
[muffled screaming]

34:15.253 --> 34:16.921
[muffled screaming]

34:37.708 --> 34:39.243
Not yet.

34:52.623 --> 34:54.025
[muffled screaming]

35:08.172 --> 35:09.907
[muffled screaming]

35:21.586 --> 35:21.953
Come on.

35:41.506 --> 35:44.242
- Can we drop it now?
QUINO: No!

35:44.308 --> 35:47.345
There must be an emergency
transformer or something.

35:47.445 --> 35:49.547
But even if there were,
we can't do anything.

35:49.647 --> 35:52.250
We have to leave
through the fucking booth.

35:52.316 --> 35:52.917
You mean, ditching Javi?

35:54.752 --> 35:57.455
That's for cowards.

35:57.522 --> 36:00.224
Are you calling me a coward?
You of all people?

36:00.758 --> 36:01.926
[sighs]

36:38.196 --> 36:39.597
What did you say?

36:44.068 --> 36:44.969
Say it again.

36:47.038 --> 36:50.641
You're a coward, Jose Zamorano.

36:50.708 --> 36:52.476
You're a fucking coward!

36:54.679 --> 36:56.047
Take it back!

37:12.129 --> 37:14.365
- Olivia.
- Yeah.

37:18.669 --> 37:19.370
I don't feel like it!

37:19.437 --> 37:22.373
[grunting]

37:28.546 --> 37:29.914
Knock it off, guys.

37:31.916 --> 37:34.352
This is not the time, damn it!

37:34.452 --> 37:36.487
- Son of a bitch!
- Hey!

37:36.554 --> 37:37.922
[Alvaro coughing]

38:08.052 --> 38:09.587
[grunts]

38:11.188 --> 38:13.024
Let go of me!

38:13.124 --> 38:15.426
Let go of me,
you piece of shit!

38:15.526 --> 38:17.161
[grunting]

38:18.229 --> 38:20.264
Of course!
Energy!

38:21.666 --> 38:22.767
Ah!

38:24.068 --> 38:26.237
Holy shit!
We are energy!

38:26.304 --> 38:28.072
We don't need to touch,
we're energy.

38:28.172 --> 38:29.507
But how do we do it?

38:29.607 --> 38:31.976
- How, how? Shit! How?
- Come on!

38:35.713 --> 38:38.716
Okay, come on,
hold this thing tight.

38:42.787 --> 38:45.690
[sobbing]
Dad!

38:45.756 --> 38:47.358
PAULA: Oh, sweetie,
are you okay?

38:47.425 --> 38:49.093
[electricity buzzing]

38:51.128 --> 38:53.130
Come on, let's go.

38:56.000 --> 38:58.936
- Come on, come on.
- Oh, my God!

39:00.004 --> 39:02.206
It's love!

39:02.273 --> 39:04.575
It's the fucking love!

39:04.642 --> 39:06.110
Alvaro! Alvaro!
Alvaro, tell him.

39:06.210 --> 39:08.279
- [grunting]
- Tell him already.

39:08.346 --> 39:11.515
Tell him what you're too scared
to say to us, even yourself.

39:11.582 --> 39:12.850
Shut up!

39:12.917 --> 39:15.086
No! No!
Tell the fucking truth, Alvaro!

39:15.152 --> 39:18.789
That you like guys.
That you like him.

39:20.424 --> 39:22.126
Let's go, run!

39:22.193 --> 39:23.694
PAULA: Run! Hurry up!

39:26.564 --> 39:29.033
[high-pitch ringing]

39:31.202 --> 39:33.104
[electricity zapping]

39:40.845 --> 39:43.114
[screaming]

39:53.290 --> 39:55.760
[screaming continues]

39:58.729 --> 40:00.164
Tell him.

40:03.467 --> 40:05.002
That you love him.

40:28.492 --> 40:30.961
[Javi panting]

40:53.150 --> 40:54.852
Yes!

40:58.889 --> 41:00.691
[panting]

41:05.396 --> 41:06.063
- Guys!
- [electrical zapping]

41:08.132 --> 41:09.733
[grunting]

41:20.845 --> 41:21.812
This way!

41:25.716 --> 41:26.917
- Get in.
MARIO: Go, go, go!

41:26.984 --> 41:28.252
Let's go!

41:28.319 --> 41:29.086
- Quickly.
PAULA: Watch your step!

41:29.153 --> 41:32.456
MARIO: Go, go!
- Careful!

41:34.425 --> 41:37.094
[straining]

41:54.411 --> 41:55.846
Quino!

42:03.087 --> 42:04.188
[Quino shouting]

42:06.590 --> 42:09.026
[screaming]

42:09.126 --> 42:11.395
- Let's go!
- No!

42:11.495 --> 42:13.330
No! Quino!

42:13.397 --> 42:14.832
No!

42:34.351 --> 42:36.086
This way.
Watch your step.

42:37.755 --> 42:39.023
Over here.

42:46.430 --> 42:47.865
Come on.

42:53.837 --> 42:56.006
No, no, no.
Mario.

42:58.609 --> 42:59.510
You stay here.

42:59.610 --> 43:00.544
- What's wrong?
- What do I do?

43:00.644 --> 43:03.480
What is it?

43:03.547 --> 43:05.849
Damn it! Damn it!

43:09.520 --> 43:10.087
Damn it!

43:12.222 --> 43:14.525
MARIO: Listen to me.

43:14.592 --> 43:17.995
Girls, take it easy, okay?
It's gonna be all right.

43:52.796 --> 43:55.399
Impossible, it's all crossroads,
it's a fucking labyrinth.

43:55.466 --> 43:57.735
- Roca was right. Fuck.
- Shit.

43:57.801 --> 44:00.004
- So, what do we do now?
- I don't know. I don't know.

44:00.070 --> 44:02.506
But we have to pick a direction,
we shouldn't stay still, Mario.

44:02.606 --> 44:05.042
And what if we get lost, huh?

44:05.109 --> 44:07.144
We are beyond that now, Mario.

44:08.712 --> 44:09.947
Oh, shit!

44:10.047 --> 44:12.916
[Spanish guitar music playing]

44:15.452 --> 44:15.953
Roca.

44:18.255 --> 44:20.891
Come on, girls, let's go.

44:20.958 --> 44:22.559
- Olivia!
- Here, hold on to me.

44:22.626 --> 44:24.895
Get up!
Here.

44:24.962 --> 44:26.397
You can do it, hurry.
Very good.

44:26.463 --> 44:29.266
Oh, God.

44:29.366 --> 44:32.202
[music continues]

44:35.773 --> 44:40.144
[man singing in Spanish]

44:40.244 --> 44:42.346
PAULA: Come on, girls,
we can do it!

44:42.446 --> 44:44.248
Just a little bit farther.

44:46.650 --> 44:48.118
Watch your step!

44:58.595 --> 44:59.363
Careful!

44:59.430 --> 45:01.632
- Mario!
MARIO: Is it here?

45:03.667 --> 45:06.236
- Mario!
- Roca!

45:06.303 --> 45:08.272
Where's Bea?
Is she with you?

45:08.372 --> 45:10.474
Yes, yes, relax,
she's fine.

45:10.574 --> 45:13.711
BEA: Dad?
- Sweetie, is that you?

45:13.811 --> 45:16.313
- Are you all right?
- Please, forgive me.

45:16.413 --> 45:17.815
I'm the one
who should apologize.

45:17.881 --> 45:20.050
- I'm sorry!
- I'm so sorry, Bea.

45:20.117 --> 45:23.320
Please forgive me.
Everything's gonna be okay.

45:23.387 --> 45:25.322
I'll get you out of there.

45:25.389 --> 45:28.158
The firemen
are on their way now!

45:28.225 --> 45:30.160
I swear, I'm gonna get you
out of there!

45:30.227 --> 45:32.496
- Do you hear me?
- Yes!

45:35.632 --> 45:37.601
[music ends]

45:37.668 --> 45:40.904
[sirens wailing]

45:53.650 --> 45:56.086
[people chattering]

46:27.851 --> 46:30.487
♪♪♪

49:01.672 --> 49:03.874
ALVARO: Javi!

49:08.845 --> 49:11.248
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

49:12.749 --> 49:15.719
It was amazing.
We saved all the girls.

49:17.254 --> 49:19.957
I mean, I almost died, but...

49:20.023 --> 49:22.559
But then,
the lights went on and...

49:23.827 --> 49:25.195
Quino?

49:31.635 --> 49:33.470
He gave us the light.

49:46.383 --> 49:47.918
[phone ringing]

50:01.164 --> 50:03.567
[ringing continues]

50:20.350 --> 50:22.786
[ringing continues]

50:34.931 --> 50:37.367
[ringing continues]

51:36.693 --> 51:39.362
[high-pitch ringing]

51:41.965 --> 51:44.434
